{"tid":6620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"準備上高登宣傳LIHKG揮手區","createTime":"2016-11-27T12:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T13:43:43.000Z","uid":11059,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10b01fda22ae00767c4702743a6f91945e01ab62","tid":6620,"uid":11059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n呢兩晚將會推出Android版<br />\n希望尚有高登會員acc既各位<br />\n一齊出post攻陷佢<br />\n呢鋪唔係高登死就係LIHKG亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTemplate:</span></span><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG 討論區正式成立，將會延續「最好用戶體驗」App<br />\n<br />\niOS 搶先下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/lihkg-tao-lun-qu/id1178373396?ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Flihkg-tao-lun-qu%2Fid1178373396%3Fls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=0GBvpCFIhN75uPy7XBKWkcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=c8d7ed69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/lihkg-tao-lun-qu/id1178373396?ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid 搶先下載：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Xxxxxxxxxxxxx</span><br />\n<br />\n&bull; 會員註冊<br />\n註冊新會員需要 ISP 或部份學校電郵認證<br />\n另外 HKG+ 用戶可以用 Plus ID 來作為邀請碼並允許任何電郵註冊<br />\n步驟：開啟「HKG+」，進入「HKG+ VIP」頁面，然後按下「點擊顯示Plus ID」<br />\n*注：由於目前 HKG+ 已經落架，所以已經刪除該 App 的用戶無法取得 Plus ID<br />\n<br />\n要令一個討論區成功，絕對唔係單靠有幾快，有幾靚就可以，而係需要一班會員，我地會非常重視你地嘅意見。<br />\nLIHKG 只係踏出左一小步，成功與否就需要靠大家。<br />\n<br />\n👆🏻🤘🏻👆🏻🤘🏻👆🏻🤘🏻👆🏻🤘🏻👆🏻<br />\n#踏上這無盡旅途"},{"pid":"0728ab60130bd31ec7b78fceb0b85a3f7a26b092","tid":6620,"uid":8755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:44:41.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96c375cb197e46830b85eec8337d42030692c79","tid":6620,"uid":11059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply